metadata.name: Granny Yaga
metadata.description:
Baba-Yaga is the popular character in Russian fairy tales. Although she is often portrayed as an evil and treacherous ancient woman with magical powers, everyone knows that she is a good grandmother at heart. Baba Yaga keeps keys to doors to other worlds, meeting with her can open new opportunities or become fatal, she is the ruler of the forest, people turn to her for advice and help, her witchcraft can be dangerous if you upset and anger the old woman. Our grandmother Yaga was born in the old Russian town of Vologda and knows the secrets of the Russian soul. She looks out the window, as if asking: Are you ready to meet the otherworld?
The first buyer of NFT will get a gift: a triptych Babushka Yaga, done in hot batik technique.
We deliver the artwork in Russia.
